These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, april, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, skateboarding, tennis, golf
City: miami, boston, hannover, liverpool
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person traveling to hannover and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person traveling to boston is the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday        | april | may  | march | january  |
| Sport         | golf    | skateboarding  | basketball       | tennis     |
| City   | hannover     | miami | liverpool       | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, lizard, mouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, reggae, pop, blues
4 different games are played: domino, whist, mah-jongg, scrabble
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
4. the person playing scrabble is between the fan blues and the owner of the mouse##2
5. the fan blues is the person playing whist##1
6. the fan soul is on the left of the person playing domino##1
7. the fan pop is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Pet         | ferret | fish    | mouse  | lizard |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | soul  | reggae   | pop    |
| Game         | whist | scrabble | domino | mah-jongg      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, garlic, cucumber, pumpkin
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, daffodil, tulip, balloon-flower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, parkour, basketball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person eating garlic##2
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food      | garlic | pumpkin         | mango   | cucumber    |
| Flower         | daffodil | balloon-flower | begonia | tulip |
| Sport   | basketball   | parkour        | cricket      | tennis   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, scientific, family
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, gamed-games, hiking, skydiving
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, game, havana, siglo
1. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is between the siglo-smoker and the person watching family movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is gamed-games##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the siglo-smoker is between the person who's hobby is singing and the game-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family        | documentary   | martial-arts | scientific |
| Hobby         | hiking | singing | gamed-games    | skydiving |
| Cigar     | havana       | oliveros     | siglo       | game    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, grey, amber, ivory
City: prague, boston, paris, san-francisco
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, western, time-travel, satire
1. the person watching satire movies is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes grey##2
2. the person watching satire movies is the person who likes ivory##1
3. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person traveling to prague##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Color   | lilac | ivory      | grey       | amber   |
| City      | prague   | boston  | san-francisco | paris     |
| Movie-Genre      | western     | satire | time-travel        | musical |

