.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, january, june, november
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, lawyer, engineer, electrician
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, siglo, oliveros, old-henry
1. the electrician is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the manager is between the electrician and the oliveros-smoker##2
6. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in june##2
7. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday    | june | january  | october | november      |
| Job   | engineer  | electrician  | manager | lawyer |
| Cigar   | old-henry | swisher | siglo | oliveros     |

