.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, prince, bongani, oliveros
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, photographer, dancer, coach
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, soy-milk, tea
1. the person drinking tea is the photographer##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the journalist##1
3. the dancer is on the far left##1
4. the coach is on the right of the dancer##1
5. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the prince-smoker is between the photographer and the dancer##2
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Cigar          | bongani  | prince    | oliveros | baccarat  |
| Job   | dancer | coach       | photographer        | journalist    |
| Beverage         | juice | cola | tea  | soy-milk |

