.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, cola, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, gospel, indie
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, motorbike, quad-bike, bus
1. the fan indie is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the fan dubstep is between the person driving the bus and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
5. the fan indie is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | lemonade  | coffee | cola | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | indie | dubstep   | gospel         |
| Transport           | roller | quad-bike  | motorbike   | bus      |

