.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, ship, boat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, crime, adventure, drama
City: nizza, prague, venice, paris
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
7. the person watching crime movies is between the person traveling to venice and the person watching disaster movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Transport          | boat  | bike    | ship | jet-ski       |
| Movie-Genre         | drama | crime | disaster  | adventure |
| City   | venice   | paris      | prague  | nizza     |

