4 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, go, canasta
House: cottage, palace, colonial, art-deco
1. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person playing bridge##2
4. the palace house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person playing go is on the far right##1
6. the palace house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the art-deco house is the person playing canasta##1
8. the cottage house is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday          | march      | october | february | november |
| Game         | canasta   | bridge  | backgammon | go |
| House   | art-deco | cottage   | palace | colonial |

