.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, roller, subway
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, almond-milk, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, dahlia, orchid
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person who growszinnia is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking almond-milk##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who growszinnia and the person driving the subway##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the person drinking tea is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Transport    | subway  | roller | quad-bike | taxi     |
| Beverage   | sprite | almond-milk   | tea  | coffee    |
| Flower     | amaryllis        | orchid       | zinnia      | dahlia |

