4. the wooden house is on the far left##1
5. the fan r&b is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the fan reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
