.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking, writing, dancing
City: boston, hannover, hamburg, edinburgh
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket, climbing, baseball
1. the person traveling to boston is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's hobby is writing##2
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby           | hiking | dancing | writing    | rock-climbing   |
| City   | hamburg      | hannover   | edinburgh | boston |
| Sport     | lacrosse     | cricket       | climbing        | baseball    |

