.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, artichoke, strawberry, apple
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, green, ebony, chestnut
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog, frog, hamster
1. the person eating strawberry is the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the hamster is the person eating apple##1
3. the person eating grapes is the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is between the person who likes blood-red and the person eating grapes##2
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Food   | strawberry   | artichoke           | grapes         | apple      |
| Color     | blood-red | ebony | chestnut | green |
| Pet   | frog     | dog         | goldfish       | hamster        |

