.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, baking, traveling
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, vegafina, dannemann, swisher
House: gothic-revival, colonial, wooden, cape-cod
1. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is baking and the colonial house##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is between the dannemann-smoker and the cape-cod house##2
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the gothic-revival house is between the wooden house and the swisher-smoker##2
7. the pall-mall-smoker is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | baking | hiking   | traveling |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | vegafina    | dannemann   | swisher     |
| House   | cape-cod  | wooden | gothic-revival | colonial   |

