.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, coral, chestnut, mauve
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, turkish, french
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, gardening, sudoku, hiking
1. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
2. the turkish is between the person who likes mauve and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
5. the japanese is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
6. the canadian is on the right of the turkish##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Color   | ebony    | coral | mauve           | chestnut |
| Nationality       | japanese | turkish    | canadian          | french   |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | gardening   | hiking | singing  |

