.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
House: tower, farmhouse, modern, wooden
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, bridge, monopoly
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, brazilian, british, spanish
1. the person playing bridge is the farmhouse house##1
2. the tower house is on the right of the polish##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the modern house##1
4. the tower house is between the person playing bridge and the person playing scrabble##2
5. the brazilian is on the left of the wooden house##1
6. the spanish is between the farmhouse house and the polish##2
7. the person playing monopoly is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| House      | modern | tower | farmhouse     | wooden   |
| Game   | scrabble | monopoly        | bridge  | snooker  |
| Nationality           | polish      | spanish         | brazilian | british |

