.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, ambient, electronic, hip-hop
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, woodworking, singing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, may, january
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
2. the fan pop is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the fan electronic is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the fan hip-hop and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre        | hip-hop | ambient | pop | electronic |
| Hobby         | chess       | drawing     | woodworking   | singing   |
| Birthday   | march | april | may | january |

 